article.headline: Ingram, Whitney-Sidney lead Lehigh over Bucknell 71-63 in OT
article.description: — Joshua Ingram scored 22 points, Tyler Whitney-Sidney gave Lehigh the lead for good with a three-point play to begin overtime and the Mountain Hawks beat the Bucknell Bison 71-63. on Monday night.
article.linkText: Ingram, Whitney-Sidney lead Lehigh over Bucknell 71-63 in OT
article.story: LEWISBURG, Pa. -- — Joshua Ingram scored 22 points, Tyler Whitney-Sidney gave Lehigh the lead for good with a three-point play to begin overtime and the Mountain Hawks beat the Bucknell Bison 71-63. on Monday night. Ingram added eight rebounds for the Mountain Hawks (9-15, 6-7 Patriot League). Burke Chebuhar scored 14 points and grabbed eight rebounds. Whitney-Sidney scored 13. Elvin Edmonds IV finished with 20 points, 10 rebounds and four assists for the Bison (10-16, 7-6). Jack Forrest added 16 points and six rebounds. Ian Motta recorded eight points and nine rebounds. Dominic Parolin made the second of two free throws with 12 seconds left to force overtime tied at 59. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
